{% doc %}
  PDP Similar Products — product grid sourced from the
  `spectrum.recommendations_similar_products_live` product metafield
  (substitute-intent recommendations written by the Similar Products LLM
  playbook). PDP-only. Off-PDP the snippet hides silently (no anchor
  product).

  Server-rendering: this snippet does NOT iterate products in Liquid. The
  metafield carries product handles only — the cards (image, title, price,
  swatches, variants) need full product objects, which the runtime fetches
  per handle via `Spectrum.products.getByHandle(handle)` on first paint.
  The snippet SSRs an N-card skeleton plus a hidden `<template>` carrying
  one card's worth of markup, and the runtime JS clones the template once
  per resolved product.

  Empty / error path: when the metafield is missing or its default entry has
  no recommendations, the SSR guard skips the snippet body entirely — no
  skeleton, no script tag. When handles are present but every per-handle
  product fetch fails at runtime, the JS flips `data-spectrum-vis="off"` on
  the snippet's outer wrapper; the fail-closed gate installed by
  `_sai-artifacts.liquid` then hides the entire snippet.

  @param {Object} variant - The resolved default variant of the snippet
    instance. Read at `variant.content` for typed prop values (heading,
    description, product_count, layout, etc.).
  @param {Object} mo - The `spectrum_snippet_instance` metaobject drop.
    Unused by this snippet body — product data comes from the
    recommendations metafield + per-handle product fetches at runtime, not
    from a typed reference pool.
  @param {String} mutation_handle - Stable handle for this instance. Consumed
    by the wrapper outer div only; not read inside this snippet body.
  @param {String} experience_handle - Studio experience handle. Consumed by
    the wrapper outer div; not read inside this snippet body.
{% enddoc %}

{%- comment -%}
  PDP Similar Products — metafield-sourced product grid, client-rendered.

  Wrapper contract (per docs/tech/studio-liquid-snippets.md and
  packages/liquid-parser/src/snippet-instance-wrapper.ts):
    - variant            default variant from mo.variants.value.variants
    - mo                 spectrum_snippet_instance metaobject drop
    - mutation_handle    consumed by wrapper outer div
    - experience_handle  consumed by wrapper outer div

  variant.content fields:
    - heading              string                section title
    - description          string                section description
    - product_count        integer 1..10         how many similar products
                           to request (Shopify caps the API limit at 10)
    - list_layout          'grid' | 'carousel' | 'list'
    - cards_per_row        { mobile, tablet?, desktop? } each integer 1..6 (mobile-first cascade)
    - progress_indicator   'none'|'scroll_bar'|'dots'|'stepper' (carousel only)
    - carousel_arrows      boolean        (carousel only)
    - image_aspect_ratio   '1/1' | '3/4' | '4/3'
    - image_object_fit     'cover' | 'contain'
    - image_mode           'single' | 'carousel'
    - show_image_dots      boolean
    - image_dots_position  'left' | 'center' | 'right'    placement of the image-carousel dot strip
    - title_lines          '1' | '2' | '3' | 'wrap'
    - show_price_label, show_current_price, show_mrp, show_discount, show_cta : booleans
    - price_label_text     string
    - cta_label            string
    - enable_navigate_to_pdp boolean                      when true, CTA navigates to PDP and Mini-PDP modal is suppressed
    - show_swatches        boolean
    - swatch_option_name   string                option name to source swatches from (case-insensitive)
    - swatch_max_visible   { mobile, tablet?, desktop? } 1..12, cap before "+N" overflow chip
    - swatch_shape         'circle' | 'square'

  Card structure (cloned by JS from `<template data-sai-card-template>`)
    <div .__card>                            ← shell, not interactive itself
      <a .__card-link href=PDP>              ← image + title + price area, click → PDP
        <div .__image-zone>                  ← aspect-ratio container
          <img .__image>     OR              ← image_mode = 'single'
          <div .__image-track>...slides...   ← image_mode = 'carousel'
        </div>
        <div .__body>
          <h3 .__title>
          [.__swatches] (when show_swatches)
          <div .__price-block>
            [.__price-label] [.__price-current] [.__price-mrp] [.__price-discount]
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      [<a .__cta href=PDP>label</a>]         ← sibling so we don't nest <a> in <a>

  Mini-PDP data: when navigate-to-PDP is off, the JS fetches /products/{handle}.js
  on first modal open per product and caches the response in a module-scope Map.
  No per-card `<script data-spectrum-atc-data>` blob is SSR'd because we don't
  have the products at server-render time.

  Anchor product: the PDP `product` global is read once to emit the anchor
  product id into the config block. Off-PDP, `product` is nil and the JS
  silently hides the wrapper on bind.

  NOTE: do not write literal Liquid tag syntax in documentation text — the
  catalog import balance check rejects nested `comment` / `doc` / control tags.
{%- endcomment -%}

{% stylesheet %}
/* Featured Collection — aggregated into spectrum-snippet.css at install */

/* Container ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sai-frpxf1zz {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
  font-family: var(--sai-font-body);
}

/* Heading + description.  Explicit font-size + color — many merchant themes
   reset bare <h2>/<p> to inherited or zero sizing via class-targeted rules
   (`.h2`, `.heading`, etc.). The `display: block !important` defends against
   themes that hide unclassed headings outright. */
.sai-frpxf1zz__heading {
  display: block !important;
  margin: 0 0 var(--sai-size-2);
  font-family: var(--sai-font-heading);
  font-style: var(--sai-font-heading-style);
  font-weight: var(--sai-font-heading-weight);
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  line-height: 1.3;
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__description {
  margin: 0 0 var(--sai-size-5);
  font-family: var(--sai-font-body);
  font-style: var(--sai-font-body-style);
  font-weight: var(--sai-font-body-weight);
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.5;
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
}

/* Layout wrapper. Carousel mode: stacks the carousel frame above the
   indicator strip. */
.sai-frpxf1zz__layout {
  display: block;
}

/* Carousel frame — wraps the scroller + arrows. Provides the positioning
   context that the absolutely-positioned arrows need so they sit centred
   over the carousel itself, not over the indicator strip below. */
.sai-frpxf1zz__frame {
  position: relative;
}

/* Grid (default) ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
/* Cards-per-row reads three viewport-keyed CSS vars set inline on this
 * element by the Liquid template (`--sai-frpxf1zz-cpr-m/-t/-d`). Mobile is
 * the base (no media query); tablet and desktop overrides kick in at the
 * same Dawn-aligned breakpoints used by the rest of this snippet's static
 * styles (750 / 990). */
.sai-frpxf1zz__grid--grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(var(--sai-frpxf1zz-cpr-m, 2), 1fr);
  gap: var(--sai-size-4);
}

@media (min-width: 750px) {
  .sai-frpxf1zz__grid--grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(var(--sai-frpxf1zz-cpr-t, 3), 1fr);
  }
}

@media (min-width: 990px) {
  .sai-frpxf1zz__grid--grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(var(--sai-frpxf1zz-cpr-d, 4), 1fr);
  }
}

/* Carousel ────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sai-frpxf1zz__grid--carousel {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: row;
  gap: var(--sai-size-4);
  overflow-x: auto;
  overflow-y: hidden;
  scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
  scrollbar-width: none;
  -ms-overflow-style: none;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__grid--carousel::-webkit-scrollbar {
  display: none;
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__grid--carousel > .sai-frpxf1zz__card {
  flex: 0 0
    calc(
      (100% - (var(--sai-frpxf1zz-cpr-m, 2) - 1) * var(--sai-size-4)) /
      var(--sai-frpxf1zz-cpr-m, 2)
    );
  scroll-snap-align: start;
  scroll-snap-stop: always;
}

@media (min-width: 750px) {
  .sai-frpxf1zz__grid--carousel > .sai-frpxf1zz__card {
    flex: 0 0
      calc(
        (100% - (var(--sai-frpxf1zz-cpr-t, 3) - 1) * var(--sai-size-4)) /
        var(--sai-frpxf1zz-cpr-t, 3)
      );
  }
}

@media (min-width: 990px) {
  .sai-frpxf1zz__grid--carousel > .sai-frpxf1zz__card {
    flex: 0 0
      calc(
        (100% - (var(--sai-frpxf1zz-cpr-d, 4) - 1) * var(--sai-size-4)) /
        var(--sai-frpxf1zz-cpr-d, 4)
      );
  }
}

/* List ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sai-frpxf1zz__grid--list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--sai-size-4);
}

/* Carousel controls ────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sai-frpxf1zz__controls {
  margin-top: var(--sai-size-3);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: var(--sai-size-3);
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__arrow {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  display: none;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 36px;
  height: 36px;
  padding: 0;
  background: var(--sai-color-bg);
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
  border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 12%, transparent);
  border-radius: 999px;
  box-shadow: var(--sai-shadow-1);
  cursor: pointer;
  z-index: 2;
  transition: opacity var(--sai-duration-1) var(--sai-ease-out-1);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__arrow svg {
  width: 16px;
  height: 16px;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__arrow--prev {
  left: var(--sai-size-2);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__arrow--next {
  right: var(--sai-size-2);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__arrow:disabled,
.sai-frpxf1zz__arrow[aria-disabled="true"] {
  opacity: 0.4;
  cursor: default;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__arrow:hover:not(:disabled) {
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-bg) 92%, var(--sai-color-fg));
}

@media (min-width: 750px) {
  .sai-frpxf1zz__layout--carousel .sai-frpxf1zz__arrow {
    display: inline-flex;
  }
}

/* Page-level dots ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sai-frpxf1zz__dots {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--sai-size-2);
  padding: 0;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__dot {
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  padding: 0;
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 25%, transparent);
  border: none;
  border-radius: 999px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background var(--sai-duration-1) var(--sai-ease-out-1), transform
    var(--sai-duration-1) var(--sai-ease-out-1);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__dot.is-active {
  background: var(--sai-color-fg);
  transform: scale(1.3);
}

/* Scroll bar ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sai-frpxf1zz__scrollbar {
  position: relative;
  width: min(240px, 60%);
  height: 3px;
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 12%, transparent);
  border-radius: 999px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
/* The thumb is an empty <div>; merchant themes (Horizon/Dawn) ship
   `div:empty { display: none }` (specificity 0,1,1) which would collapse it to
   0×0 and the scroll-position indicator would silently never appear. Scoping
   under `.__scrollbar` lifts this to (0,2,0) so it outranks that reset WITHOUT
   `!important` — per-instance baked rules (0,3,0) still win the cascade. */
.sai-frpxf1zz__scrollbar .sai-frpxf1zz__scrollbar-thumb {
  display: block;
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  height: 100%;
  width: 25%;
  background: var(--sai-color-fg);
  border-radius: 999px;
  transform: translateX(0%);
  transition: transform var(--sai-duration-2) var(--sai-ease-out-1);
}

/* Stepper ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sai-frpxf1zz__stepper {
  font-size: 0.8125rem;
  font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 70%, transparent);
}

/* Card shell ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sai-frpxf1zz__card {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  /* Cards in the same grid row stretch to equal height via CSS Grid's default
     align-items: stretch. `justify-content: space-between` pushes the CTA to
     the card's bottom edge so a card with a short title doesn't end up with
     its ATC button floating mid-card next to siblings with longer titles. */
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: var(--sai-size-3);
  padding: var(--sai-size-3);
  background: transparent;
  border-radius: var(--sai-radius-lg);
  transition: box-shadow var(--sai-duration-2) var(--sai-ease-out-1), transform
    var(--sai-duration-2) var(--sai-ease-out-1);
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__card:hover {
  box-shadow: var(--sai-shadow-2);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__card-link {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--sai-size-3);
  text-decoration: none;
  color: inherit;
}

/* Image zone ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sai-frpxf1zz__image-zone {
  position: relative;
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  overflow: hidden;
  border-radius: var(--sai-radius-md);
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 6%, transparent);
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__image {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  transition: transform var(--sai-duration-3) var(--sai-ease-out-1);
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__card:hover .sai-frpxf1zz__image {
  transform: scale(1.03);
}

/* Per-card image carousel ─────────────────────────────────── */
.sai-frpxf1zz__image-zone--carousel {
  position: relative;
  padding: 0;
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__image-track {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: row;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  overflow-x: auto;
  overflow-y: hidden;
  scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
  scrollbar-width: none;
  -ms-overflow-style: none;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__image-track::-webkit-scrollbar {
  display: none;
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__image-slide {
  position: relative;
  flex: 0 0 100%;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  scroll-snap-align: start;
  scroll-snap-stop: always;
}

/* Disable card-level hover zoom in carousel mode — fights swipe. */
.sai-frpxf1zz__card:hover .sai-frpxf1zz__image-zone--carousel .sai-frpxf1zz__image {
  transform: none;
}

/* Image dots — `data-position` is set by the snippet from the
 * `image_dots_position` prop. Default (center) keeps the existing
 * 50%/translateX strategy; left/right anchor to the same inset and
 * drop the centering transform. */
.sai-frpxf1zz__image-dots {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: var(--sai-size-2);
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  padding: 4px 8px;
  background: rgb(0 0 0 / 0.35);
  border-radius: 999px;
  pointer-events: auto;
  z-index: 1;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__image-dots[data-position="left"] {
  left: var(--sai-size-2);
  right: auto;
  transform: none;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__image-dots[data-position="right"] {
  left: auto;
  right: var(--sai-size-2);
  transform: none;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__image-dot {
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;
  padding: 0;
  background: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.55);
  border: none;
  border-radius: 999px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background var(--sai-duration-1) var(--sai-ease-out-1), transform
    var(--sai-duration-1) var(--sai-ease-out-1);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__image-dot.is-active {
  background: #fff;
  transform: scale(1.35);
}

/* Body ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sai-frpxf1zz__body {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--sai-size-2);
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__title {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: var(--sai-font-body);
  font-weight: var(--sai-font-body-weight);
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  line-height: 1.35;
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
  display: -webkit-box !important;
  -webkit-box-orient: vertical !important;
  -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
  overflow: hidden !important;
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__title[data-title-lines="1"] {
  -webkit-line-clamp: 1;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__title[data-title-lines="2"] {
  -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__title[data-title-lines="3"] {
  -webkit-line-clamp: 3;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__title[data-title-lines="wrap"] {
  display: block !important;
  overflow: visible !important;
  -webkit-line-clamp: unset;
}

/* Swatches ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── *
 * Per-viewport visibility is driven by `data-hide-m/-t/-d`
 * attributes baked at render time. Mobile is the base (those with
 * `data-hide-m` are hidden on mobile); tablet and desktop overrides
 * use the same Dawn-aligned 750 / 990 breakpoints as the rest of
 * this snippet's static CSS. The three `--m/-t/-d` overflow chips
 * are independently gated so only the active viewport's chip shows. */
.sai-frpxf1zz__swatches {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: nowrap;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--sai-size-2);
  margin-top: var(--sai-size-1);
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__swatch {
  display: inline-block;
  width: 16px;
  height: 16px;
  flex: 0 0 auto;
  background-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 8%, var(--sai-color-bg));
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 18%, transparent);
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__swatches--circle .sai-frpxf1zz__swatch {
  border-radius: 999px;
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__swatches--square .sai-frpxf1zz__swatch {
  border-radius: 2px;
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__swatch-more {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  min-width: 18px;
  padding: 0 4px;
  font-size: 11px;
  line-height: 1;
  color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 70%, transparent);
  border-radius: 999px;
  background-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 8%, var(--sai-color-bg));
}

/* Per-viewport gating. Mobile is the base — `data-hide-m` swatches and the
 * tablet/desktop overflow chips are hidden by default. Each `@media` block
 * un-hides the next viewport's set and hides the previous viewport's chip. */
.sai-frpxf1zz__swatch[data-hide-m],
.sai-frpxf1zz__swatch-more--t,
.sai-frpxf1zz__swatch-more--d {
  display: none;
}

@media (min-width: 750px) {
  .sai-frpxf1zz__swatch[data-hide-m] {
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .sai-frpxf1zz__swatch[data-hide-t] {
    display: none;
  }
  .sai-frpxf1zz__swatch-more--m {
    display: none;
  }
  .sai-frpxf1zz__swatch-more--t {
    display: inline-flex;
  }
}

@media (min-width: 990px) {
  .sai-frpxf1zz__swatch[data-hide-t] {
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .sai-frpxf1zz__swatch[data-hide-d] {
    display: none;
  }
  .sai-frpxf1zz__swatch-more--t {
    display: none;
  }
  .sai-frpxf1zz__swatch-more--d {
    display: inline-flex;
  }
}

/* Price block ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sai-frpxf1zz__price-block {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--sai-size-1);
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__price-label {
  font-size: 0.6875rem;
  line-height: 1.3;
  color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 60%, transparent);
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__price-row {
  display: inline-flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: var(--sai-size-2);
  align-items: baseline;
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__price-current {
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: var(--sai-font-body-weight-bold);
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__price-mrp {
  font-size: 0.8125rem;
  color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 50%, transparent);
  text-decoration: line-through;
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__price-discount {
  font-size: 0.6875rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--sai-color-error, #1d9e75);
  padding: 0;
  background: transparent;
  border-radius: var(--sai-radius-sm);
}

/* CTA ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sai-frpxf1zz__cta {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 100%;
  padding: var(--sai-size-2) var(--sai-size-3);
  font-family: var(--sai-font-body);
  font-size: 0.8125rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  text-align: center;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: var(--sai-color-primary-fg);
  background: var(--sai-color-primary);
  border: none;
  border-radius: var(--sai-radius-md);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background var(--sai-duration-1) var(--sai-ease-out-1);
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__cta:hover,
.sai-frpxf1zz__cta:focus-visible {
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-primary) 88%, var(--sai-color-fg));
}

/* Sold-out: every variant on this product returned `available: false`.
   The JS swaps the label to the merchant-configured sold-out copy and adds
   `is-soldout` + `aria-disabled`.  Dimmed, no hover affordance, no clicks. */
.sai-frpxf1zz__cta.is-soldout,
.sai-frpxf1zz__cta[aria-disabled="true"] {
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 14%, var(--sai-color-bg));
  color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 55%, transparent);
  cursor: not-allowed;
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   Mini-PDP — full quick-view modal
   Mobile (< 750px): bottom sheet.  Desktop: centred modal.
   ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 9999;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-end;
  justify-content: center;
  font-family: var(--sai-font-body);
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp[hidden] {
  display: none;
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-backdrop {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: rgb(0 0 0 / 0.5);
  animation: sai-frpxf1zz-fade-in var(--sai-duration-2) var(--sai-ease-out-1);
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-panel {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  width: 100%;
  max-height: 92vh;
  overflow-y: auto;
  background: var(--sai-color-bg);
  border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
  box-shadow: 0 -8px 32px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.18);
  animation: sai-frpxf1zz-slide-up var(--sai-duration-2) var(--sai-ease-out-1);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--radius-sharp .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-panel {
  border-radius: 0;
}

@media (min-width: 750px) {
  .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp {
    align-items: center;
  }
  .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-panel {
    max-height: 88vh;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.24);
    animation: sai-frpxf1zz-fade-in var(--sai-duration-2) var(--sai-ease-out-1);
  }
  .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--radius-sharp .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-panel {
    border-radius: 0;
  }
  .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--width-sm .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-panel {
    width: min(640px, 92vw);
  }
  .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--width-md .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-panel {
    width: min(880px, 92vw);
  }
  .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--width-lg .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-panel {
    width: min(1080px, 92vw);
  }
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-close {
  position: absolute;
  top: var(--sai-size-3);
  right: var(--sai-size-3);
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 32px;
  height: 32px;
  padding: 0;
  background: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.9);
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
  border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 12%, transparent);
  border-radius: 999px;
  cursor: pointer;
  z-index: 3;
  transition: background var(--sai-duration-1) var(--sai-ease-out-1);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-close svg {
  width: 14px;
  height: 14px;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-close:hover {
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-bg) 90%, var(--sai-color-fg));
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-layout {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}
@media (min-width: 750px) {
  .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-carousel .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-layout {
    flex-direction: row;
  }
  .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-carousel .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-gallery {
    flex: 1 1 50%;
  }
  .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-carousel .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-content {
    flex: 1 1 50%;
  }
}

/* Gallery */
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-gallery {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 5%, transparent);
  overflow: hidden;
}
/* List-mode (compact thumbnail) gallery — Frido-style header layout:
   square thumbnail on the left, title + price on the right; secondary
   content (variants / low stock / qty / description / CTAs) flows below
   full-width. CSS Grid with `display: contents` on the inner content
   wrapper lets us project all the children onto the grid as siblings of
   the gallery so we can place each precisely while keeping the existing
   Liquid markup. */
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-list .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-layout {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr;
  align-items: start;
  column-gap: var(--sai-size-4);
  row-gap: var(--sai-size-3);
  padding: var(--sai-size-4);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-list .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-gallery {
  width: 140px;
  height: 140px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  margin: 0;
  grid-column: 1;
  grid-row: 1 / span 2;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-list .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-content {
  display: contents;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-list .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-title {
  grid-column: 2;
  grid-row: 1;
  margin: 0;
  min-width: 0;
  font-family: var(--sai-font-body);
  font-size: 1.0625rem;
  font-weight: 600;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-list .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-price-row {
  grid-column: 2;
  grid-row: 2;
  margin: 0;
  min-width: 0;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-list .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variants,
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-list .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-low-stock,
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-list .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-qty,
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-list .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-description,
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-list .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-ctas {
  grid-column: 1 / -1;
  margin: 0;
  min-width: 0;
}
@media (min-width: 750px) {
  .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-list .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-layout {
    grid-template-columns: 160px 1fr;
  }
  .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-list .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-gallery {
    width: 160px;
    height: 160px;
  }
}

/* Discount badge → pastel-green pill on its own line below the price. */
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-list .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-discount {
  flex-basis: 100%;
  align-self: flex-start;
  margin-top: 6px;
  padding: 4px 12px;
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-error, #1d9e75) 18%, transparent);
  color: var(--sai-color-error, #1d9e75);
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 600;
}

/* List mode: keep the CTAs as a 2-up row (Add To Cart + Buy Now) at
   equal widths so the full-width CTA strip below the thumbnail reads as a
   single primary action row, not stacked buttons. */
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-list .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-ctas {
  flex-direction: row;
  gap: var(--sai-size-2);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-list .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-ctas > * {
  flex: 1 1 0;
  min-width: 0;
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-track {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: row;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  overflow-x: auto;
  overflow-y: hidden;
  scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
  scrollbar-width: none;
  -ms-overflow-style: none;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-track::-webkit-scrollbar {
  display: none;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-slide {
  position: relative;
  flex: 0 0 100%;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  scroll-snap-align: start;
  scroll-snap-stop: always;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-slide img {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
}

/* Chevrons */
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-chevron {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 36px;
  height: 36px;
  padding: 0;
  background: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.92);
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
  border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 12%, transparent);
  border-radius: 999px;
  box-shadow: var(--sai-shadow-1);
  cursor: pointer;
  z-index: 2;
  transition: opacity var(--sai-duration-1) var(--sai-ease-out-1);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-chevron[hidden] {
  display: none;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-chevron svg {
  width: 16px;
  height: 16px;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-chevron--prev {
  left: var(--sai-size-3);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-chevron--next {
  right: var(--sai-size-3);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-chevron:disabled,
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-chevron[aria-disabled="true"] {
  opacity: 0.4;
  cursor: default;
}

/* Pagination dots */
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-dots {
  position: absolute;
  left: 50%;
  bottom: var(--sai-size-3);
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  padding: 4px 8px;
  background: rgb(0 0 0 / 0.4);
  border-radius: 999px;
  z-index: 1;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-dots[hidden] {
  display: none;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-dot {
  width: 7px;
  height: 7px;
  padding: 0;
  background: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.55);
  border: none;
  border-radius: 999px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background var(--sai-duration-1) var(--sai-ease-out-1), transform
    var(--sai-duration-1) var(--sai-ease-out-1);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-dot.is-active {
  background: #fff;
  transform: scale(1.35);
}

/* Overlay actions */
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-overlay-actions {
  position: absolute;
  top: var(--sai-size-3);
  right: var(--sai-size-3);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--sai-size-2);
  z-index: 2;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-list .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-overlay-actions {
  display: none;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-share,
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-view-product {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 36px;
  height: 36px;
  padding: 0;
  background: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.92);
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
  border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 12%, transparent);
  border-radius: 999px;
  cursor: pointer;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background var(--sai-duration-1) var(--sai-ease-out-1);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-share svg,
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-view-product svg {
  width: 16px;
  height: 16px;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-share:hover,
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-view-product:hover {
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-bg) 88%, var(--sai-color-fg));
}

/* Content zone */
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-content {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--sai-size-3);
  padding: var(--sai-size-4) var(--sai-size-4) var(--sai-size-5);
}
@media (min-width: 750px) {
  .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-carousel .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-content {
    padding: var(--sai-size-5) var(--sai-size-5);
    overflow-y: auto;
  }
}

/* Price row */
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-price-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: var(--sai-size-2);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-price-current {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: var(--sai-font-body-weight-bold);
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-price-mrp[hidden] {
  display: none;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-price-mrp {
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 50%, transparent);
  text-decoration: line-through;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-discount[hidden] {
  display: none;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-discount {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--sai-color-error, #1d9e75);
  padding: 2px 6px;
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-error, #1d9e75) 12%, transparent);
  border-radius: var(--sai-radius-sm);
}

/* Title */
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-title {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: var(--sai-font-heading);
  font-style: var(--sai-font-heading-style);
  font-weight: var(--sai-font-heading-weight);
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  line-height: 1.3;
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
}
@media (min-width: 750px) {
  .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-carousel .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
}

/* Variant selector */
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variants {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: var(--sai-size-2);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variants--dropdown {
  display: block;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variants--pill .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variant {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 4px;
  min-height: 38px;
  padding: 6px 14px;
  background: var(--sai-color-bg);
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 18%, transparent);
  border-radius: 999px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: border-color var(--sai-duration-1) var(--sai-ease-out-1), background
    var(--sai-duration-1) var(--sai-ease-out-1);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variants--pill .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variant.is-selected {
  border-color: var(--sai-color-fg);
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 4%, transparent);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variants--pill .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variant:disabled,
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variants--pill .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variant[aria-disabled="true"] {
  opacity: 0.45;
  cursor: not-allowed;
  text-decoration: line-through;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variants--swatch .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variant {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  min-width: 44px;
  min-height: 44px;
  padding: 6px 10px;
  background: var(--sai-color-bg);
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
  font-size: 0.8125rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 18%, transparent);
  border-radius: var(--sai-radius-sm);
  cursor: pointer;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variants--swatch .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variant.is-selected {
  border-color: var(--sai-color-fg);
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 4%, transparent);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variants--swatch .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variant:disabled {
  opacity: 0.45;
  cursor: not-allowed;
  text-decoration: line-through;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variants--dropdown select {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 10px 12px;
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  background: var(--sai-color-bg);
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
  border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 18%, transparent);
  border-radius: var(--sai-radius-md);
  cursor: pointer;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variant-price {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 60%, transparent);
}

/* Low inventory */
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-low-stock[hidden] {
  display: none;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-low-stock {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  font-size: 0.8125rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--sai-color-error, #d23f3f);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-low-stock svg {
  width: 14px;
  height: 14px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

/* Quantity */
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-qty {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--sai-size-3);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-qty-label {
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-qty-stepper {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 18%, transparent);
  border-radius: var(--sai-radius-md);
  overflow: hidden;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-qty-button {
  width: 36px;
  height: 36px;
  padding: 0;
  background: var(--sai-color-bg);
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
  border: none;
  font-size: 1rem;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background var(--sai-duration-1) var(--sai-ease-out-1);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-qty-button:hover {
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 6%, transparent);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-qty-input {
  width: 44px;
  height: 36px;
  padding: 0;
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  text-align: center;
  background: var(--sai-color-bg);
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
  border: none;
  border-left: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 18%, transparent);
  border-right: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 18%, transparent);
  -moz-appearance: textfield;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-qty-input::-webkit-outer-spin-button,
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-qty-input::-webkit-inner-spin-button {
  -webkit-appearance: none;
  margin: 0;
}

/* Description */
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-description--font-sm .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-description-body {
  font-size: 0.8125rem;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-description--font-md .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-description-body {
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  line-height: 1.55;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-description-body {
  color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 80%, transparent);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-description--compact .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-description-body {
  display: -webkit-box;
  -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
  -webkit-line-clamp: 3;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-description--expandable.is-collapsed .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-description-body {
  display: -webkit-box;
  -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
  -webkit-line-clamp: 3;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-description-toggle[hidden] {
  display: none;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-description-toggle {
  margin-top: 4px;
  padding: 0;
  background: transparent;
  border: none;
  font-size: 0.8125rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
  cursor: pointer;
  text-decoration: underline;
}

/* CTA buttons */
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-ctas {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--sai-size-3);
  margin-top: auto;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-ctas--side_by_side {
  flex-direction: row;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-ctas--side_by_side > * {
  flex: 1 1 0;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-ctas--stacked {
  flex-direction: column;
}
@media (min-width: 750px) {
  .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-carousel .sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-ctas {
    margin-top: var(--sai-size-4);
  }
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-atc,
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-buy-now {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 14px 20px;
  font-family: var(--sai-font-body);
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  border-radius: var(--sai-radius-md);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background var(--sai-duration-1) var(--sai-ease-out-1);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-atc {
  background: var(--sai-color-primary);
  color: var(--sai-color-primary-fg);
  border: 1px solid var(--sai-color-primary);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-atc:hover:not(:disabled) {
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-primary) 88%, var(--sai-color-fg));
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-atc:disabled,
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-buy-now:disabled {
  opacity: 0.5;
  cursor: not-allowed;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-buy-now {
  background: var(--sai-color-bg);
  color: var(--sai-color-fg);
  border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 35%, transparent);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-buy-now:hover:not(:disabled) {
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 4%, transparent);
}

/* Loading state — buttons that fire async cart writes set `aria-busy="true"`
   while the request is in flight.  The label fades to transparent and a
   rotating spinner overlays the center so the button stays clickable size
   without text-jump. */
.sai-frpxf1zz__cta[aria-busy="true"],
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-atc[aria-busy="true"],
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-buy-now[aria-busy="true"] {
  color: transparent !important;
  pointer-events: none;
  position: relative;
  opacity: 1 !important;
  cursor: progress !important;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__cta[aria-busy="true"]::after,
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-atc[aria-busy="true"]::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  width: 18px;
  height: 18px;
  margin: -9px 0 0 -9px;
  border: 2.5px solid var(--sai-color-primary-fg);
  border-top-color: transparent;
  border-radius: 50%;
  opacity: 1;
  animation: sai-frpxf1zz-spin 0.7s linear infinite;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-buy-now[aria-busy="true"]::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  width: 18px;
  height: 18px;
  margin: -9px 0 0 -9px;
  border: 2.5px solid var(--sai-color-fg);
  border-top-color: transparent;
  border-radius: 50%;
  opacity: 1;
  animation: sai-frpxf1zz-spin 0.7s linear infinite;
}
/* Skeleton shimmer — applied to image-zone + title + price-block on cards
   carrying the `--skeleton` modifier (SSR'd loading placeholders, removed
   from the DOM once their slot's resolved product is painted in). Uses a
   single horizontal sweeping highlight in `currentColor` at low opacity
   so the effect honours theme dark/light surfaces without needing a
   second token. `will-change: background-position` lets the compositor
   handle the gradient slide without repainting the card. Respects
   `prefers-reduced-motion`. */
.sai-frpxf1zz__card--skeleton .sai-frpxf1zz__image-zone,
.sai-frpxf1zz__title--skeleton,
.sai-frpxf1zz__price-block--skeleton {
  position: relative;
  background-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 8%, transparent);
  background-image: linear-gradient(
    90deg,
    transparent 0%,
    color-mix(in srgb, var(--sai-color-fg) 6%, transparent) 50%,
    transparent 100%
  );
  background-size: 200% 100%;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-position: 100% 0;
  animation: sai-frpxf1zz-shimmer 1.4s linear infinite;
  will-change: background-position;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.sai-frpxf1zz__title--skeleton {
  height: 0.9em;
  border-radius: var(--sai-radius-sm);
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__title--skeleton[data-title-lines="2"] {
  height: 2em;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__title--skeleton[data-title-lines="3"] {
  height: 3em;
}
.sai-frpxf1zz__price-block--skeleton {
  height: 1.25em;
  border-radius: var(--sai-radius-sm);
}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .sai-frpxf1zz__card--skeleton .sai-frpxf1zz__image-zone,
  .sai-frpxf1zz__title--skeleton,
  .sai-frpxf1zz__price-block--skeleton {
    animation: none;
    background-image: none;
  }
}

@keyframes sai-frpxf1zz-shimmer {
  from { background-position: 100% 0; }
  to   { background-position: -100% 0; }
}

@keyframes sai-frpxf1zz-spin {
  to {
    transform: rotate(360deg);
  }
}

@keyframes sai-frpxf1zz-fade-in {
  from {
    opacity: 0;
  }
  to {
    opacity: 1;
  }
}
@keyframes sai-frpxf1zz-slide-up {
  from {
    transform: translateY(100%);
  }
  to {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
}

.sai-frpxf1zz-body-locked {
  overflow: hidden !important;
}
{% endstylesheet %}

{%- assign content = variant.content -%}
{%- assign heading = content.heading | default: '' -%}
{%- assign description = content.description | default: '' -%}

{%- comment -%}── Layout mode: whitelist, default grid ──{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign layout = content.list_layout | default: 'grid' -%}
{%- unless layout == 'grid' or layout == 'carousel' or layout == 'list' -%}
  {%- assign layout = 'grid' -%}
{%- endunless -%}

{%- comment -%}
  Cards-per-row: viewport-keyed object `{ mobile, tablet?, desktop? }`. Mobile
  is the cascade base. Each slot clamps to 1..6 with sensible defaults; tablet
  and desktop fall back to the next-smaller viewport when unset so authors can
  set one value and let the cascade flow.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign cpr_raw = content.cards_per_row -%}
{%- assign cpr_m = cpr_raw.mobile -%}
{%- assign cpr_t = cpr_raw.tablet -%}
{%- assign cpr_d = cpr_raw.desktop -%}
{%- if cpr_m == nil or cpr_m == blank -%}{%- assign cpr_m = 2 -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if cpr_t == nil or cpr_t == blank -%}{%- assign cpr_t = cpr_m -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if cpr_d == nil or cpr_d == blank -%}{%- assign cpr_d = cpr_t -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if cpr_m < 1 -%}{%- assign cpr_m = 1 -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if cpr_m > 6 -%}{%- assign cpr_m = 6 -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if cpr_t < 1 -%}{%- assign cpr_t = 1 -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if cpr_t > 6 -%}{%- assign cpr_t = 6 -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if cpr_d < 1 -%}{%- assign cpr_d = 1 -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if cpr_d > 6 -%}{%- assign cpr_d = 6 -%}{%- endif -%}

{%- comment -%}── Product count: clamp to 1..10 (Shopify recommendations API cap), default 8 ──{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign product_count = content.product_count -%}
{%- if product_count == nil or product_count == blank -%}
  {%- assign product_count = 8 -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- if product_count < 1 -%}{%- assign product_count = 1 -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if product_count > 10 -%}{%- assign product_count = 10 -%}{%- endif -%}

{%- comment -%}── Carousel-only options. Whitelisted; ignored when layout != 'carousel'. ──{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign indicator = content.progress_indicator | default: 'none' -%}
{%- unless indicator == 'none' or indicator == 'scroll_bar' or indicator == 'dots' or indicator == 'stepper' -%}
  {%- assign indicator = 'none' -%}
{%- endunless -%}
{%- if content.carousel_arrows == nil -%}{%- assign carousel_arrows = true -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign carousel_arrows = content.carousel_arrows -%}{%- endif -%}

{%- comment -%}── Image aspect-ratio: whitelist, default 1/1 ──{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign aspect = content.image_aspect_ratio | default: '1/1' -%}
{%- unless aspect == '1/1' or aspect == '3/4' or aspect == '4/3' -%}
  {%- assign aspect = '1/1' -%}
{%- endunless -%}

{%- comment -%}── Image object-fit: whitelist, default cover ──{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign fit = content.image_object_fit | default: 'cover' -%}
{%- unless fit == 'cover' or fit == 'contain' -%}
  {%- assign fit = 'cover' -%}
{%- endunless -%}

{%- comment -%}── Image mode: 'single' (default) renders the featured image;
   'carousel' renders all product images (cap 8) as a swipeable strip. ──{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign image_mode = content.image_mode | default: 'single' -%}
{%- unless image_mode == 'single' or image_mode == 'carousel' -%}
  {%- assign image_mode = 'single' -%}
{%- endunless -%}
{%- if content.show_image_dots == nil -%}{%- assign show_image_dots = true -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign show_image_dots = content.show_image_dots -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- assign image_dots_position = content.image_dots_position | default: 'center' -%}
{%- unless image_dots_position == 'left' or image_dots_position == 'center' or image_dots_position == 'right' -%}
  {%- assign image_dots_position = 'center' -%}
{%- endunless -%}

{%- comment -%}── Title lines: '1'|'2'|'3'|'wrap', default '2' ──{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign title_lines = content.title_lines | default: '2' -%}
{%- unless title_lines == '1' or title_lines == '2' or title_lines == '3' or title_lines == 'wrap' -%}
  {%- assign title_lines = '2' -%}
{%- endunless -%}

{%- comment -%}── Visibility booleans ──{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if content.show_price_label == nil -%}{%- assign show_price_label = false -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign show_price_label = content.show_price_label -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if content.show_current_price == nil -%}{%- assign show_current_price = true -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign show_current_price = content.show_current_price -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if content.show_mrp == nil -%}{%- assign show_mrp = true -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign show_mrp = content.show_mrp -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if content.show_discount == nil -%}{%- assign show_discount = true -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign show_discount = content.show_discount -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if content.show_cta == nil -%}{%- assign show_cta = true -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign show_cta = content.show_cta -%}{%- endif -%}

{%- assign price_label_text = content.price_label_text | default: '' -%}
{%- assign sold_out_label = content.sold_out_label | default: 'Sold Out' -%}
{%- comment -%}
  `cta_label` resolution is deferred to AFTER `enable_navigate_to_pdp` is
  read below — its value depends on which CTA mode is active.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- comment -%}
  Swatches: optional row of color dots under each card title. Source data is
  Shopify's product option values; we read `.swatch.color` / `.swatch.image`
  when Shopify exposes them (Online Store 2.0+ with the option set to
  "Color" in admin), otherwise the swatch renders as a neutral disc.
  `swatch_max_visible` is responsive; per-viewport caps are emitted into the
  rendered DOM as `data-hide-m/-t/-d` attributes and resolved by CSS.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if content.show_swatches == nil -%}
  {%- assign show_swatches = false -%}
{%- else -%}
  {%- assign show_swatches = content.show_swatches -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- assign swatch_option_name = content.swatch_option_name | default: 'Color' -%}
{%- assign swatch_shape = content.swatch_shape | default: 'circle' -%}
{%- unless swatch_shape == 'circle' or swatch_shape == 'square' -%}
  {%- assign swatch_shape = 'circle' -%}
{%- endunless -%}

{%- comment -%}── Swatch caps: same mobile-first cascade as cards_per_row ──{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign smv_raw = content.swatch_max_visible -%}
{%- assign smv_m = smv_raw.mobile -%}
{%- assign smv_t = smv_raw.tablet -%}
{%- assign smv_d = smv_raw.desktop -%}
{%- if smv_m == nil or smv_m == blank -%}{%- assign smv_m = 3 -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if smv_t == nil or smv_t == blank -%}{%- assign smv_t = smv_m -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if smv_d == nil or smv_d == blank -%}{%- assign smv_d = smv_t -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if smv_m < 1 -%}{%- assign smv_m = 1 -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if smv_m > 12 -%}{%- assign smv_m = 12 -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if smv_t < 1 -%}{%- assign smv_t = 1 -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if smv_t > 12 -%}{%- assign smv_t = 12 -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if smv_d < 1 -%}{%- assign smv_d = 1 -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if smv_d > 12 -%}{%- assign smv_d = 12 -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- assign smv_max = smv_m -%}
{%- if smv_t > smv_max -%}{%- assign smv_max = smv_t -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if smv_d > smv_max -%}{%- assign smv_max = smv_d -%}{%- endif -%}

{%- comment -%}
  Master Mini-PDP gate. When `enable_navigate_to_pdp` is true the CTA loses
  its JS interception (no `data-spectrum-atc`), the per-card payload script
  is skipped, and the Mini-PDP modal block at the bottom of the snippet is
  not rendered. The merchant-facing prop sheet hides every Mini-PDP config
  under the toggle in this mode.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if content.enable_navigate_to_pdp == nil -%}
  {%- assign enable_navigate_to_pdp = false -%}
{%- else -%}
  {%- assign enable_navigate_to_pdp = content.enable_navigate_to_pdp -%}
{%- endif -%}

{%- comment -%}
  Two CTA labels co-exist in variant.content so the merchant can word the
  button differently for the two CTA modes. `cta_label` is used when the
  CTA opens the Mini-PDP / adds to cart; `cta_label_navigate` is used when
  the CTA is a pure anchor to the product detail page. The schema exposes
  exactly one of the two fields in the prop sheet based on
  `enable_navigate_to_pdp`, so a stored value for the inactive mode is
  preserved across toggles.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if enable_navigate_to_pdp -%}
  {%- assign cta_label = content.cta_label_navigate | default: 'View details' -%}
{%- else -%}
  {%- assign cta_label = content.cta_label | default: 'Add to cart' -%}
{%- endif -%}

{%- comment -%}── Mini-PDP props — whitelist + default everything ──{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign pdp_gallery_style = content.pdp_gallery_style | default: 'carousel' -%}
{%- unless pdp_gallery_style == 'carousel' or pdp_gallery_style == 'list' -%}
  {%- assign pdp_gallery_style = 'carousel' -%}
{%- endunless -%}
{%- assign pdp_gallery_aspect_ratio = content.pdp_gallery_aspect_ratio | default: '1/1' -%}
{%- unless pdp_gallery_aspect_ratio == '1/1' or pdp_gallery_aspect_ratio == '3/4' or pdp_gallery_aspect_ratio == '4/3' or pdp_gallery_aspect_ratio == '16/9' -%}
  {%- assign pdp_gallery_aspect_ratio = '1/1' -%}
{%- endunless -%}
{%- if content.pdp_show_chevrons == nil -%}{%- assign pdp_show_chevrons = true -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign pdp_show_chevrons = content.pdp_show_chevrons -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if content.pdp_show_dots == nil -%}{%- assign pdp_show_dots = true -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign pdp_show_dots = content.pdp_show_dots -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if content.pdp_auto_play == nil -%}{%- assign pdp_auto_play = false -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign pdp_auto_play = content.pdp_auto_play -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- assign pdp_modal_max_width = content.pdp_modal_max_width | default: 'md' -%}
{%- unless pdp_modal_max_width == 'sm' or pdp_modal_max_width == 'md' or pdp_modal_max_width == 'lg' -%}
  {%- assign pdp_modal_max_width = 'md' -%}
{%- endunless -%}
{%- assign pdp_modal_border_radius = content.pdp_modal_border_radius | default: 'rounded' -%}
{%- unless pdp_modal_border_radius == 'rounded' or pdp_modal_border_radius == 'sharp' -%}
  {%- assign pdp_modal_border_radius = 'rounded' -%}
{%- endunless -%}
{%- if content.pdp_show_selling_price == nil -%}{%- assign pdp_show_selling_price = true -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign pdp_show_selling_price = content.pdp_show_selling_price -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if content.pdp_show_mrp == nil -%}{%- assign pdp_show_mrp = true -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign pdp_show_mrp = content.pdp_show_mrp -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if content.pdp_show_discount_badge == nil -%}{%- assign pdp_show_discount_badge = true -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign pdp_show_discount_badge = content.pdp_show_discount_badge -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- assign pdp_discount_format = content.pdp_discount_format | default: 'percent' -%}
{%- unless pdp_discount_format == 'percent' or pdp_discount_format == 'amount' -%}
  {%- assign pdp_discount_format = 'percent' -%}
{%- endunless -%}
{%- if content.pdp_show_view_product_cta == nil -%}{%- assign pdp_show_view_product_cta = false -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign pdp_show_view_product_cta = content.pdp_show_view_product_cta -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if content.pdp_show_share_button == nil -%}{%- assign pdp_show_share_button = false -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign pdp_show_share_button = content.pdp_show_share_button -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if content.pdp_show_variant_selector == nil -%}{%- assign pdp_show_variant_selector = true -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign pdp_show_variant_selector = content.pdp_show_variant_selector -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- assign pdp_variant_selector_style = content.pdp_variant_selector_style | default: 'pill' -%}
{%- unless pdp_variant_selector_style == 'pill' or pdp_variant_selector_style == 'dropdown' or pdp_variant_selector_style == 'swatch' -%}
  {%- assign pdp_variant_selector_style = 'pill' -%}
{%- endunless -%}
{%- if content.pdp_show_price_in_variant == nil -%}{%- assign pdp_show_price_in_variant = false -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign pdp_show_price_in_variant = content.pdp_show_price_in_variant -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if content.pdp_show_low_inventory_callout == nil -%}{%- assign pdp_show_low_inventory_callout = false -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign pdp_show_low_inventory_callout = content.pdp_show_low_inventory_callout -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- assign pdp_low_inventory_threshold = content.pdp_low_inventory_threshold | default: 10 -%}
{%- if pdp_low_inventory_threshold < 1 -%}{%- assign pdp_low_inventory_threshold = 1 -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- assign pdp_low_inventory_text = content.pdp_low_inventory_text | default: 'Only {n} available' -%}
{%- if content.pdp_show_quantity_selector == nil -%}{%- assign pdp_show_quantity_selector = false -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign pdp_show_quantity_selector = content.pdp_show_quantity_selector -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if content.pdp_show_description == nil -%}{%- assign pdp_show_description = false -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign pdp_show_description = content.pdp_show_description -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- assign pdp_description_style = content.pdp_description_style | default: 'compact' -%}
{%- unless pdp_description_style == 'compact' or pdp_description_style == 'expandable' -%}
  {%- assign pdp_description_style = 'compact' -%}
{%- endunless -%}
{%- assign pdp_description_font_size = content.pdp_description_font_size | default: 'sm' -%}
{%- unless pdp_description_font_size == 'sm' or pdp_description_font_size == 'md' -%}
  {%- assign pdp_description_font_size = 'sm' -%}
{%- endunless -%}
{%- if content.pdp_show_add_to_cart == nil -%}{%- assign pdp_show_add_to_cart = true -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign pdp_show_add_to_cart = content.pdp_show_add_to_cart -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- assign pdp_atc_label = content.pdp_atc_label | default: 'Add To Cart' -%}
{%- if content.pdp_show_buy_now == nil -%}{%- assign pdp_show_buy_now = true -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign pdp_show_buy_now = content.pdp_show_buy_now -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- assign pdp_buy_now_label = content.pdp_buy_now_label | default: 'Buy Now' -%}
{%- assign pdp_cta_layout = content.pdp_cta_layout | default: 'side_by_side' -%}
{%- unless pdp_cta_layout == 'side_by_side' or pdp_cta_layout == 'stacked' -%}
  {%- assign pdp_cta_layout = 'side_by_side' -%}
{%- endunless -%}

{%- comment -%}
  Anchor product — read from the PDP `product` global. Off-PDP, the global
  is nil and we skip the entire render. The recommendations endpoint is
  scoped per product; without an anchor there is nothing to ask for.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign anchor_id = '' -%}
{%- assign anchor_handle = '' -%}
{%- if product and product.id -%}
  {%- assign anchor_id = product.id -%}
  {%- assign anchor_handle = product.handle -%}
{%- endif -%}

{%- comment -%}
  SSR empty-state guard. The recommendations metafield is available at
  Liquid render time, so we can decide whether this snippet has anything
  to show BEFORE emitting markup. Walking the SlotEnvelope here mirrors
  what the runtime asset does inside `data-spectrum-sim-recommendations`:
  find the default slot, then the default entry within it, and check
  whether its `content.recommendations` list is non-empty.

  Why this matters even though the IIFE also calls `hideWrapper` on the
  empty path: between SSR paint and IIFE execution there is a visible
  window (skeleton cards + heading) that the runtime SDK exposes by
  flipping the wrapper's `data-spectrum-vis` to `"on"`. On themes that
  block / strip the IIFE script entirely the empty body never collapses.
  Gating the wrapper body on a server-known signal removes both failure
  modes; the IIFE's `hideWrapper` stays as the defense for the tail
  case where handles exist but every product fetch fails.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign has_recommendations = false -%}
{%- assign sim_envelope_pre = product.metafields.spectrum.recommendations_similar_products_live.value -%}
{%- if sim_envelope_pre -%}
  {%- for slot_item in sim_envelope_pre -%}
    {%- if has_recommendations -%}{%- break -%}{%- endif -%}
    {%- if slot_item.slotKey == 'default' and slot_item.payload and slot_item.payload.entries -%}
      {%- for entry in slot_item.payload.entries -%}
        {%- if entry.isDefault and entry.content and entry.content.recommendations -%}
          {%- if entry.content.recommendations.size > 0 -%}
            {%- assign has_recommendations = true -%}
          {%- endif -%}
          {%- break -%}
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    {%- endif -%}
  {%- endfor -%}
{%- endif -%}

{%- if anchor_id != '' and has_recommendations -%}
  <div class="sai-frpxf1zz sai-frpxf1zz--align-{{ align }}" data-spectrum-sim-root>
    {%- if heading != blank -%}
      <h2 class="sai-frpxf1zz__heading">{{ heading | escape }}</h2>
    {%- endif -%}
    {%- if description != blank -%}
      <p class="sai-frpxf1zz__description">{{ description | escape }}</p>
    {%- endif -%}

    <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__layout sai-frpxf1zz__layout--{{ layout }}"
         data-layout="{{ layout }}"
         data-indicator="{{ indicator }}">
      <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__frame">
      <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__grid sai-frpxf1zz__grid--{{ layout }}" style="--sai-frpxf1zz-cpr-m: {{ cpr_m }}; --sai-frpxf1zz-cpr-t: {{ cpr_t }}; --sai-frpxf1zz-cpr-d: {{ cpr_d }}" data-spectrum-sim-grid>
      {%- comment -%}
        Skeleton placeholders, one per requested product slot. JS replaces
        each in place with a populated card clone of the template below,
        and removes any leftover skeletons when Shopify returns fewer
        products than requested.
      {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- for i in (1..product_count) -%}
        <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__card sai-frpxf1zz__card--skeleton" aria-hidden="true" data-spectrum-sim-skeleton>
          <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__image-zone" style="aspect-ratio: {{ aspect }};"></div>
          <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__body">
            <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__title sai-frpxf1zz__title--skeleton" data-title-lines="{{ title_lines }}"></div>
            {%- if show_price_label or show_current_price or show_mrp or show_discount -%}
              <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__price-block sai-frpxf1zz__price-block--skeleton"></div>
            {%- endif -%}
          </div>
        </div>
      {%- endfor -%}
      </div>

      {%- if layout == 'carousel' and carousel_arrows -%}
        <button type="button"
                class="sai-frpxf1zz__arrow sai-frpxf1zz__arrow--prev"
                aria-label="Previous"
                data-spectrum-carousel-arrow="prev">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M10 3.5L5.5 8L10 12.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </button>
        <button type="button"
                class="sai-frpxf1zz__arrow sai-frpxf1zz__arrow--next"
                aria-label="Next"
                data-spectrum-carousel-arrow="next">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M6 3.5L10.5 8L6 12.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </button>
      {%- endif -%}
      </div>

      {%- if layout == 'carousel' and indicator != 'none' -%}
        {%- comment -%}
          Indicator slots are pre-rendered for `product_count` to keep the
          visual stable on first paint. After the recommendations fetch
          resolves, JS reconciles dot count + stepper denominator with
          the actual number of returned products.
        {%- endcomment -%}
        <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__controls" data-card-count="{{ product_count }}" data-spectrum-carousel-controls>
          {%- if indicator == 'dots' -%}
            <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__dots" role="tablist" aria-label="Carousel position" data-spectrum-carousel-dots>
              {%- for n in (1..product_count) -%}
                <button type="button"
                        class="sai-frpxf1zz__dot{% if forloop.first %} is-active{% endif %}"
                        aria-label="Go to slide {{ forloop.index }}"
                        data-spectrum-carousel-dot="{{ forloop.index0 }}"
                        {%- if forloop.first %} aria-selected="true"{% endif -%}></button>
              {%- endfor -%}
            </div>
          {%- elsif indicator == 'scroll_bar' -%}
            <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__scrollbar" aria-hidden="true">
              <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__scrollbar-thumb" data-spectrum-carousel-thumb></div>
            </div>
          {%- elsif indicator == 'stepper' -%}
            <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__stepper" aria-live="polite" data-spectrum-carousel-stepper>1 / {{ product_count }}</div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>

    {%- comment -%}
      Card template — cloned by JS once per returned product. Prop-driven
      structural branches (image_mode, show_swatches, show_*price*, show_cta)
      are baked at SSR; per-product fields are empty placeholders identified
      by `data-sai-*` hooks and filled by JS. Elements that may stay empty
      for a given product (image-dots when one image, swatches when no
      color option, mrp/discount when not on sale) ship `hidden` by default
      and JS unhides only when a value is set.
    {%- endcomment -%}
    <template data-spectrum-sim-card-template>
      <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__card">
        <a class="sai-frpxf1zz__card-link" href="#" data-sai-card-link>
          {%- if image_mode == 'carousel' -%}
            <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__image-zone sai-frpxf1zz__image-zone--carousel" style="aspect-ratio: {{ aspect }};">
              <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__image-track" data-spectrum-image-track></div>
              {%- if show_image_dots -%}
                <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__image-dots"
                     role="tablist"
                     aria-label="Choose product image"
                     data-position="{{ image_dots_position }}"
                     data-spectrum-image-dots
                     hidden></div>
              {%- endif -%}
            </div>
          {%- else -%}
            <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__image-zone" style="aspect-ratio: {{ aspect }};">
              <img class="sai-frpxf1zz__image"
                   src=""
                   alt=""
                   style="object-fit: {{ fit }};"
                   loading="lazy"
                   data-sai-image
                   hidden>
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
          <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__body">
            <h3 class="sai-frpxf1zz__title" data-title-lines="{{ title_lines }}" data-sai-title></h3>
            {%- if show_swatches -%}
              <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__swatches sai-frpxf1zz__swatches--{{ swatch_shape }}"
                   role="list"
                   aria-label="Available colors"
                   data-sai-swatches
                   hidden></div>
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if show_price_label or show_current_price or show_mrp or show_discount -%}
              <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__price-block">
                {%- if show_price_label and price_label_text != blank -%}
                  <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__price-label">{{ price_label_text | escape }}</div>
                {%- endif -%}
                <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__price-row">
                  {%- if show_current_price -%}
                    <span class="sai-frpxf1zz__price-current" data-sai-price-current></span>
                  {%- endif -%}
                  {%- if show_mrp -%}
                    <span class="sai-frpxf1zz__price-mrp" data-sai-price-mrp hidden></span>
                  {%- endif -%}
                  {%- if show_discount -%}
                    <span class="sai-frpxf1zz__price-discount" data-sai-price-discount hidden></span>
                  {%- endif -%}
                </div>
              </div>
            {%- endif -%}
          </div>
        </a>
        {%- if show_cta -%}
          {%- comment -%}
            When navigate-to-PDP is on, the CTA is a pure `<a href>` with no
            data attributes. Merchant themes often delegate clicks on
            `[data-product-id]` (added at runtime by this snippet's JS when
            recommendations resolve) to a global ATC handler — emitting any
            of those attrs would cause the theme to intercept the click and
            hijack the navigation back into a cart-add. In navigate mode
            the JS also short-circuits on the missing `data-sai-cta` and
            never patches in `data-product-id`.
          {%- endcomment -%}
          <a class="sai-frpxf1zz__cta"
             href="#"
             {%- unless enable_navigate_to_pdp -%}
             data-spectrum-atc
             data-sai-cta
             data-sold-out-label="{{ sold_out_label | escape }}"
             {%- endunless -%}>{{ cta_label | escape }}</a>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
    </template>

    {%- comment -%}
      Mini-PDP — full quick-view modal. Hidden until JS opens it. Lives
      outside the layout block so its `position: fixed` styling doesn't
      fight the layout/grid. Per-product data is fetched lazily from
      `/products/{handle}.js` on first open and cached client-side; the
      modal renders skeleton content until that fetch resolves.
    {%- endcomment -%}
    {%- if show_cta and enable_navigate_to_pdp == false -%}
      <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--gallery-{{ pdp_gallery_style }} sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--width-{{ pdp_modal_max_width }} sai-frpxf1zz__pdp--radius-{{ pdp_modal_border_radius }}"
           data-spectrum-pdp-modal
           hidden>
        <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-backdrop" data-spectrum-pdp-backdrop></div>
        <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-panel"
             role="dialog"
             aria-modal="true"
             aria-labelledby="sai-frpxf1zz-pdp-title"
             data-spectrum-pdp-panel>

          <button type="button"
                  class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-close"
                  data-spectrum-pdp-close
                  aria-label="Close">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M3 3l10 10M13 3L3 13" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
          </button>

          <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-layout">
            <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-gallery"
                 style="aspect-ratio: {{ pdp_gallery_aspect_ratio }};"
                 data-spectrum-pdp-gallery>
              <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-track" data-spectrum-pdp-track></div>

              {%- if pdp_show_chevrons -%}
                <button type="button"
                        class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-chevron sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-chevron--prev"
                        data-spectrum-pdp-chevron="prev"
                        aria-label="Previous image"
                        hidden>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M10 3.5L5.5 8L10 12.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                </button>
                <button type="button"
                        class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-chevron sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-chevron--next"
                        data-spectrum-pdp-chevron="next"
                        aria-label="Next image"
                        hidden>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M6 3.5L10.5 8L6 12.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                </button>
              {%- endif -%}

              {%- if pdp_show_dots -%}
                <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-dots" role="tablist" aria-label="Gallery position" data-spectrum-pdp-dots hidden></div>
              {%- endif -%}

              <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-overlay-actions">
                {%- if pdp_show_share_button -%}
                  <button type="button"
                          class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-share"
                          data-spectrum-pdp-share
                          aria-label="Share product">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
                      <circle cx="3" cy="8" r="2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/>
                      <circle cx="12" cy="3.5" r="2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/>
                      <circle cx="12" cy="12.5" r="2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/>
                      <path d="M5 7L10 4M5 9L10 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/>
                    </svg>
                  </button>
                {%- endif -%}
                {%- if pdp_show_view_product_cta -%}
                  <a class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-view-product"
                     href="#"
                     data-spectrum-pdp-view-product
                     aria-label="View full product page">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
                      <path d="M9 2h5v5M14 2L8 8M12 9v4a1 1 0 01-1 1H3a1 1 0 01-1-1V5a1 1 0 011-1h4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                    </svg>
                  </a>
                {%- endif -%}
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-content">

              <h3 class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-title"
                  id="sai-frpxf1zz-pdp-title"
                  data-spectrum-pdp-title></h3>

              {%- if pdp_show_selling_price or pdp_show_mrp or pdp_show_discount_badge -%}
                <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-price-row" data-spectrum-pdp-price-row>
                  {%- if pdp_show_selling_price -%}
                    <span class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-price-current" data-spectrum-pdp-price-current></span>
                  {%- endif -%}
                  {%- if pdp_show_mrp -%}
                    <span class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-price-mrp" data-spectrum-pdp-price-mrp hidden></span>
                  {%- endif -%}
                  {%- if pdp_show_discount_badge -%}
                    <span class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-discount" data-spectrum-pdp-discount hidden></span>
                  {%- endif -%}
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}

              {%- if pdp_show_variant_selector -%}
                <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variants sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-variants--{{ pdp_variant_selector_style }}"
                     data-spectrum-pdp-variants
                     role="radiogroup"
                     aria-label="Choose a variant"></div>
              {%- endif -%}

              {%- if pdp_show_low_inventory_callout -%}
                <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-low-stock"
                     data-spectrum-pdp-low-stock
                     role="status"
                     hidden>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
                    <path d="M8 1.5l1 4 4 .5-3 3 1 4-3-2-3 2 1-4-3-3 4-.5z" fill="currentColor"/>
                  </svg>
                  <span data-spectrum-pdp-low-stock-text></span>
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}

              {%- if pdp_show_quantity_selector -%}
                <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-qty" data-spectrum-pdp-qty-row>
                  <label class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-qty-label" for="sai-frpxf1zz-pdp-qty">Quantity</label>
                  <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-qty-stepper">
                    <button type="button" class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-qty-button" data-spectrum-pdp-qty-decrement aria-label="Decrease quantity">−</button>
                    <input id="sai-frpxf1zz-pdp-qty"
                           class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-qty-input"
                           type="number"
                           min="1"
                           step="1"
                           value="1"
                           data-spectrum-pdp-qty-input
                           inputmode="numeric">
                    <button type="button" class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-qty-button" data-spectrum-pdp-qty-increment aria-label="Increase quantity">+</button>
                  </div>
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}

              {%- if pdp_show_description -%}
                <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-description sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-description--{{ pdp_description_style }} sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-description--font-{{ pdp_description_font_size }}"
                     data-spectrum-pdp-description>
                  <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-description-body" data-spectrum-pdp-description-body></div>
                  {%- if pdp_description_style == 'expandable' -%}
                    <button type="button"
                            class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-description-toggle"
                            data-spectrum-pdp-description-toggle
                            aria-expanded="false"
                            hidden>Read more</button>
                  {%- endif -%}
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}

              {%- if pdp_show_add_to_cart or pdp_show_buy_now -%}
                <div class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-ctas sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-ctas--{{ pdp_cta_layout }}">
                  {%- if pdp_show_buy_now -%}
                    <button type="button"
                            class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-buy-now"
                            data-spectrum-pdp-buy-now>{{ pdp_buy_now_label | escape }}</button>
                  {%- endif -%}
                  {%- if pdp_show_add_to_cart -%}
                    <button type="button"
                            class="sai-frpxf1zz__pdp-atc"
                            data-spectrum-pdp-atc>{{ pdp_atc_label | escape }}</button>
                  {%- endif -%}
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <script type="application/json" data-spectrum-pdp-config>
          {
            "galleryStyle": {{ pdp_gallery_style | json }},
            "showChevrons": {{ pdp_show_chevrons | json }},
            "showDots": {{ pdp_show_dots | json }},
            "autoPlay": {{ pdp_auto_play | json }},
            "showSellingPrice": {{ pdp_show_selling_price | json }},
            "showMrp": {{ pdp_show_mrp | json }},
            "showDiscountBadge": {{ pdp_show_discount_badge | json }},
            "discountFormat": {{ pdp_discount_format | json }},
            "showVariantSelector": {{ pdp_show_variant_selector | json }},
            "variantSelectorStyle": {{ pdp_variant_selector_style | json }},
            "showPriceInVariant": {{ pdp_show_price_in_variant | json }},
            "showLowInventoryCallout": {{ pdp_show_low_inventory_callout | json }},
            "lowInventoryThreshold": {{ pdp_low_inventory_threshold | json }},
            "lowInventoryText": {{ pdp_low_inventory_text | json }},
            "showQuantitySelector": {{ pdp_show_quantity_selector | json }},
            "showDescription": {{ pdp_show_description | json }},
            "descriptionStyle": {{ pdp_description_style | json }},
            "soldOutLabel": {{ sold_out_label | json }}
          }
        </script>
      </div>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>
  {%- comment -%}
    Recommendation handles, resolved server-side from the
    `spectrum.recommendations_similar_products_live` product metafield.
    Shape on disk is the standard SlotEnvelope (array of slot items, each
    with `payload.entries[]`); the runtime renders the default entry only,
    so we walk to the first `entry.isDefault` and emit its
    `content.recommendations` as a flat handle array. Empty / missing
    metafield yields an empty `[]`, which the runtime treats as the
    silent-hide signal.
  {%- endcomment -%}
  {%- assign similar_envelope = product.metafields.spectrum.recommendations_similar_products_live.value -%}
  <script type="application/json" data-spectrum-sim-recommendations>
[
{%- if similar_envelope -%}
  {%- assign emitted = false -%}
  {%- for slot_item in similar_envelope -%}
    {%- if emitted -%}{%- break -%}{%- endif -%}
    {%- if slot_item.slotKey == 'default' and slot_item.payload and slot_item.payload.entries -%}
      {%- for entry in slot_item.payload.entries -%}
        {%- if entry.isDefault and entry.content and entry.content.recommendations -%}
          {%- for handle in entry.content.recommendations -%}
            {%- unless forloop.first -%},{%- endunless -%}
            {{ handle | json }}
          {%- endfor -%}
          {%- assign emitted = true -%}
          {%- break -%}
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    {%- endif -%}
  {%- endfor -%}
{%- endif -%}
]
  </script>
  {%- comment -%}
    Anchor + prop bag for the runtime asset. Drives the card-template
    population pass (image rendering, swatches, price formatting, Mini-PDP
    config). The product list itself comes from the
    `data-spectrum-sim-recommendations` block above. Every interpolated
    value pipes through `| json` so storefront text and merchant config
    can't escape the surrounding `<script>` element.
  {%- endcomment -%}
  <script type="application/json" data-spectrum-sim-config>
    {
      "anchorProductId": {{ anchor_id | json }},
      "anchorProductHandle": {{ anchor_handle | json }},
      "productCount": {{ product_count | json }},
      "intent": "related",
      "layout": {{ layout | json }},
      "indicator": {{ indicator | json }},
      "imageMode": {{ image_mode | json }},
      "imageObjectFit": {{ fit | json }},
      "imageAspect": {{ aspect | json }},
      "showImageDots": {{ show_image_dots | json }},
      "imageDotsPosition": {{ image_dots_position | json }},
      "titleLines": {{ title_lines | json }},
      "showCurrentPrice": {{ show_current_price | json }},
      "showMrp": {{ show_mrp | json }},
      "showDiscount": {{ show_discount | json }},
      "showCta": {{ show_cta | json }},
      "ctaLabel": {{ cta_label | json }},
      "soldOutLabel": {{ sold_out_label | json }},
      "enableNavigateToPdp": {{ enable_navigate_to_pdp | json }},
      "showSwatches": {{ show_swatches | json }},
      "swatchOptionName": {{ swatch_option_name | json }},
      "swatchMaxVisible": {
        "mobile": {{ smv_m | json }},
        "tablet": {{ smv_t | json }},
        "desktop": {{ smv_d | json }}
      },
      "swatchShape": {{ swatch_shape | json }}
    }
  </script>
  {%- comment -%}
    Asset only loads when the wrapper rendered (anchor present). The IIFE
    has no work without a container; off-PDP pages skip the entire block
    above and never request this script.
  {%- endcomment -%}
  <script src="{{ 'sai-snippet-frpxf1zz.js' | asset_url }}" async></script>
{%- endif -%}
